	"html": "<a id=\"t.c499591d59d336b0142b6c9bafa444e4b0d0f50c\"></a><a id=\"t.0\"></a><h2 class=\"c1\" id=\"h.jkykwfdq9hrc\"><span class=\"c16\">What’s Up in (the first 2 weeks of) June?</span></h2><p class=\"c20\"><span class=\"c7\">With the arrival of 1.24 million doses of AZ vaccine donated by the Japanese government, vaccination continues across Taiwan. False and suspicious narratives related to vaccine and vaccination have been observed during the first 2 weeks of June.</span></p><a id=\"t.85412ea872dceb7ddcf3d6c2d8594f26db1cc77b\"></a><a id=\"t.1\"></a><div class=\"gdoc-table-container\"><div class=\"table\"><table class=\"c4\"><tbody><tr class=\"c12\"><th class=\"c5 c18\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c20\"><span class=\"c0\">Suspicious narratives</span></p></th><th class=\"c5 c18\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c13\"><span class=\"c0\">Features</span></p></th><th class=\"c5 c18 ccp china\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c13\"><span class=\"c0\">Dissemination nodes</span></p><ul class=\"c10 lst-kix_tkkg2d8xsk2f-0 start\"><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-1\"><span class=\"c0\">CCP</span></li><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-2\"><span class=\"c0\">China</span></li><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-2\"><span class=\"c0\">Other</span></li></ul></th><th class=\"c5 c18\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c13\"><span class=\"c0\">Clarification, fact-checking</span></p></th></tr><tr class=\"c12\"><td class=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c13\"><span class=\"c0\">Taiwanese go to China to get vaccinated</span></p></td><td class=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c10 lst-kix_gs82bi14woyu-0 start\"><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-1\"><span class=\"c0\">Involvement of Chinese state media and authority</span></li><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-1\"><span class=\"c0\">📢 Propoganda</span></li></ul></td><td class=\"ccp china\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c10 lst-kix_3rbuzqwbsqr-0 start\"><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-1\"><span class=\"c6\"><a class=\"c3\" href=\"https://www.globaltimes.cn/page/202106/1225752.shtml\">環球時報</a></span><span class=\"c0\">&nbsp;{{ccp}}</span></li><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-1\"><span class=\"c6\"><a class=\"c3\" href=\"http://www.gwytb.gov.cn/xwdt/xwfb/wyly/202106/t20210611_12358743.htm\">國台辦</a></span><span class=\"c0\">&nbsp;{{ccp}}</span></li></ul></td><td class=\"no\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c13\"><span class=\"c0\">None</span></p></td></tr><tr class=\"c12\"><td class=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c13\"><span class=\"c0\">Taiwan to donate vaccines to diplomatic allies</span></p></td><td class=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c10 lst-kix_ip437otfjl1e-0 start\"><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-1\"><span class=\"c0\">Initiated by Chinese state media</span></li><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-1\"><span class=\"c0\">❌ False info</span></li></ul></td><td class=\"ccp china\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c10 lst-kix_4x88wivh1n45-0 start\"><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-2\"><span class=\"c6\"><a class=\"c3\" href=\"https://taiwan.huanqiu.com/article/43Pt9GT1ATo\">環球時報</a></span><span class=\"c0\">&nbsp;{{ccp}}</span></li></ul></td><td class=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c10 lst-kix_i71vicga2erl-0 start\"><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-1\"><span class=\"c6\"><a class=\"c3\" href=\"https://www.mofa.gov.tw/News_Content.aspx?n=95&amp;s=95952\">台灣外交部</a></span></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"c12\"><td class=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c13\"><span class=\"c0\">Taiwan pork tested with ractopamine in Hong Kong</span></p></td><td class=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c10 lst-kix_ifv8ih1lde7i-0 start\"><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-2\"><span class=\"c0\">Initiated by Chinese state media</span></li><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-1\"><span class=\"c0\">❌ False info</span></li></ul></td><td class=\"ccp china\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c10 lst-kix_bxekgh133yqz-0 start\"><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-1\"><span class=\"c21\">香港</span><span class=\"c6\"><a class=\"c3\" href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2021/06/03/YO2106030001.htm\">文匯報</a></span><span class=\"c0\">&nbsp;{{ccp}}</span></li></ul></td><td class=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c10 lst-kix_wxprld2sx19f-0 start\"><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-1\"><span class=\"c6\"><a class=\"c3\" href=\"https://www.coa.gov.tw/theme_data.php?theme=news&amp;sub_theme=agri&amp;id=8411\">台灣農委會</a></span></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"c12\"><td class=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c13\"><span class=\"c0\">Japanese foreign minister says Taiwan doesn’t need many vaccines</span></p></td><td class=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c10 lst-kix_8h8pp5oahkxq-0 start\"><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-1\"><span class=\"c0\">❌ False info</span></li></ul></td><td class=\"ccp china\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c10 lst-kix_ddt88udj1lui-0 start\"><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-2\"><span class=\"c6\"><a class=\"c3\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Geekfirm/posts/10159323269421460\">朱學恒</a></span></li></ul></td><td class=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c10 lst-kix_xl8zyoksb5xh-0 start\"><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-2\"><span class=\"c21\">台灣事實查核中心</span><span class=\"c6\"><a class=\"c3\" href=\"https://tfc-taiwan.org.tw/articles/5738\">報吿 #1027</a></span></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"c12\"><td class=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c13\"><span class=\"c0\">Taiwan-produced Medigen vaccine and Moderna are like twins that have the same origin</span></p></td><td class=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c10 lst-kix_8h8pp5oahkxq-0\"><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-1\"><span class=\"c0\">❌ False info</span></li></ul></td><td class=\"ccp china\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c10 lst-kix_lxc4jd7mfw4y-0 start\"><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-2\"><span class=\"c6\"><a class=\"c3\" href=\"https://www.gvm.com.tw/article/76100\">遠見雜誌</a></span></li><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-1\"><span class=\"c6\"><a class=\"c3\" href=\"https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20201117fin008/\">鏡週刊</a></span></li><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-1\"><span class=\"c6\"><a class=\"c3\" href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com.tw/b5/20201124/video/283789.html?%E9%AB%98%E7%AB%AF%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%88%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%95%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%9C%9F%E8%A9%A6%E9%A9%97%20%E6%8B%9A%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B45.6%E6%9C%88%E5%95%8F%E4%B8%96\">新唐人</a></span></li></ul></td><td class=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c10 lst-kix_awf7vbmrcdhi-0 start\"><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-2\"><span class=\"c21\">台灣事實查核中心</span><span class=\"c6\"><a class=\"c3\" href=\"https://tfc-taiwan.org.tw/articles/5691\">報告 #1016</a></span></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"c12\"><td class=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c13\"><span class=\"c0\">US company Blackwater invests in the development of Taiwanese vaccine UB-612</span></p></td><td class=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c10 lst-kix_it6gow6cv56p-0 start\"><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-1\"><span class=\"c0\">⚠️ Suspicious info</span></li></ul></td><td class=\"ccp china\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c10 lst-kix_gyzxgy3bdole-0 start\"><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-1\"><span class=\"c6\"><a class=\"c3\" href=\"https://weibo.com/7010131150/KiQab0NVb?type=comment#_rnd1623816341443\">帝吧官微</a></span><span class=\"c0\">&nbsp;{{china}}</span></li><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-1\"><span class=\"c6\"><a class=\"c3\" href=\"https://youtu.be/SvyAfPk7jX8\">新聞大白話</a></span></li><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-1\"><span class=\"c6\"><a class=\"c3\" href=\"https://youtu.be/OEXPVFLX62o\">108 演播室</a></span></li><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-1\"><span class=\"c6\"><a class=\"c3\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SisyWorldNews/posts/4173963362681310\">文茜的世界周報</a></span></li><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-2\"><span class=\"c6\"><a class=\"c3\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HaungZX/posts/333277628159103\">黃智賢世界</a></span></li></ul></td><td class=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c10 lst-kix_gsngt4nk72x6-0 start\"><li class=\"c11 li-bullet-1\"><span class=\"c21\">Cofacts 真的假的</span><span class=\"c6\"><a class=\"c3\" href=\"https://cofacts.tw/article/8cc2yq0adgxw\">編輯意見</a></span></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><p class=\"c20\"><span>The CCP continues to use vaccines as a propaganda tool against Taiwan. But its tone has changed from last month’s harsh criticism to a softer appeal since the beginning of June. In last week’s report, IORG had found that the CCP disseminated narratives such as “America hasn’t sold a single dose of vaccines to Taiwan” and “The DPP’s refusal to open up for Chinese vaccines is due to political demons” in an attempt to divide Taiwan-US relations. But in the first two weeks of June, the theme has changed to “Taiwanese go to China to get vaccinated.” For example, Chinese state media Global Times cites the words of XU </span><span>Zheng-wen</span><span class=\"c7\">&nbsp;(徐正文), head of Taiwanese Chamber of Commerce in China, that getting vaccinated in China is more convenient than doing it in America. The spokesperson of China’s Taiwan Affairs Office also claims that “There have been 62,000 Taiwanese vaccinated in China.”</span></p><a id=\"t.2f2806de34c0ebc4a2678a68fd5894383ab4e487\"></a><a id=\"t.2\"></a><div class=\"gdoc-note\"><div class=\"detail\"><p class=\"c19\"><span class=\"c7\">XU Zheng-wen (徐正文) is a former member of the Central Committee of the KMT and a former guest member of the Beijing Municipal Committee. He provoked controversy in February 2020 by inserting people who caught COVID-19 to a group that took a designated plane heading back to Taiwan.</span></p></div></div><p class=\"c20\"><span class=\"c7\">根據 IORG 資料庫，6 月前 2 週共有至少 320 則提及「台灣人到中國打疫苗」的 Facebook 華語粉專貼文，單日數量以 6 月 11 日最多，共有 70 則，內容多提及國台辦當日發言。另外，有 162 則 Facebook 貼文提及蕭敬騰、潘美辰、孟庭葦、陳志朋、王耀慶、溫嵐等台灣藝人到中國打疫苗，蕭敬騰就佔了 129 則（79.63%）。台灣藝人到中國打疫苗與中共論述呼應，可能影響台灣民眾對「到中國打疫苗」的觀感。</span></p><p class=\"c20\"><span>中共一方面利用台灣目前對疫苗的迫切需求打出溫情攻勢，另一方面以官媒發出錯誤訊息。《環球時報》報導「岛内疫苗严重紧缺，民进党当局却欲将 30 万剂阿斯利康疫苗转赠友邦」，隔日我國外交部即回應，此說法為錯誤言論；香港《文匯報》報導台灣豬肉品牌製品在香港被驗出萊克多巴胺超標，這則報導與香港政府食環署檢驗結果矛盾，我國農委會亦已於隔日澄清，但仍有 52 則 Facebook 華語貼文傳播此論述，並有11 個粉專直接引用《文匯報》的微博貼文內容，包括「</span><span class=\"c8\"><a class=\"c3\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/366417997378868_780524062634924\">村長詹江村全球後援會粉絲團</a></span><span>」、「</span><span class=\"c8\"><a class=\"c3\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/president168168/posts/534576631310105\">庶民選總統～唯一支持韓國瑜</a></span><span>」、「</span><span class=\"c8\"><a class=\"c3\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=5526400487434049&amp;id=949685718438905\">黃復興台中市支黨部</a></span><span class=\"c7\">」等泛藍政治立場粉專。</span></p><p class=\"c20\"><span class=\"c7\">上一期週報的「不心慌預報」，IORG 提醒疫苗相關可疑言論將持續出現，在過去 2 週間，的確發現相關訊息。其中有 2 則錯誤訊息：「日本外相說台灣政府不想要太多疫苗」、「高端、莫德納疫苗系出同門」，1 則可疑訊息：「美國黑水公司投資聯亞疫苗研發」錯誤引用路透社報導，質疑美國將台灣人當成疫苗實驗對象。這些錯誤、可以訊息都可能誤導台灣民眾對疫苗的正確認知。</span></p><p class=\"c20\"><span>IORG 提醒，未來可能出現「不要打日本疫苗」、「不要打國產疫苗」、「疫苗分配不公平」相關資訊操弄。隨著日本外相在 6 月 15 日</span><span class=\"c8\"><a class=\"c3\" href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202106155005.aspx\">表示</a></span><span class=\"c7\">考慮追加疫苗給台灣後，日本提供台灣的疫苗「是日本不要的」、「過期的」、「不安全」，此類詆毀日本 AZ 疫苗的資訊操弄可能持續出現。高端疫苗解盲後，國產疫苗「不安全」、「打了不能出國」等說法，則可能使閱聽大眾產生「不要打國產疫苗」的想法，影響防疫。</span></p><div class=\"separator\"></div><a id=\"t.ddc8da8f14956e0838fde572a21f3dff62665921\"></a><a id=\"t.3\"></a><div class=\"gdoc-photo-container\"><div class=\"images\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/mUnjZw9SpbHcBP1coCY8vv5WKnjBcexp2NIHPRmre0u0kgRZkuerBWegIKoydf2l8AmLA1zMgagT0AXDj2OzE61DN-MyH2eXoUhA7ooneONMp6HJMjc2wH30CO37L2cORA\" title=\"\"></div></div><div class=\"separator\"></div><p class=\"c20\"><span>Full version of this Dokidoki Alert Weekly is available in Taiwanese Mandarin. Please visit </span><span class=\"c8\"><a class=\"c3\" href=\"https://iorg.tw/da/2\">https://iorg.tw/da/2</a></span><span class=\"c7\">&nbsp;for more...</span></p>",
